OL,5, A national helpline for victims of     
OL,6, modern slavery is reporting a steep    
OL,7, rise in contact from overseas workers  
OL,8, who came to the UK to help plug        
OL,9, staffing gaps in the care sector.      
OL,11,FMany said they had paid huge sums to   
OL,12,Fthe people who brought them over after 
OL,13,Fvisa rules changed last year.          
OL,15,FUnseen UK said more than 700 care staff
OL,16,Fused its helpline in 2022.             
OL,18,FMinisters say they "strongly condemn"  
OL,19,Foffering foreign care workers          
OL,20,Femployment "under false pretences".    
